ğŸ§± What is a Class?

A class is like a blueprint or template to create objects.
It defines the structure (attributes) and behavior (methods) of an object.

ğŸ“¦ Example:

class Employee {
    String name;
    int age;
    double salary;

    void getSalary() {
        // logic to return salary
    }

    void increment() {
        // logic to increase salary
    }
}


