ğŸ”‘ OOPS Terminology

1. Abstraction

â†’ Hiding the internal details [ Show only essential info ]
Real Example: Use this phone without bothering about how it was made.

â¸»

2. Encapsulation

â†’ The act of putting various components together (in a capsule)
Example: Laptop is a single entity with WiFi + Speaker + Storage in a single box!
In Java, encapsulation simply means that the sensitive data can be hidden from the users.

â¸»

3. Inheritance

â†’ The act of deriving new things from existing things
Examples:
Rickshaw â†’ E-Rickshaw
Phone â†’ SmartPhone
Implement DRY!

â¸»

4. Polymorphism

â†’ One entity, many forms
Examples:
SmartPhone â†’ Phone
SmartPhone â†’ Calculator
SmartPhone â†’ Camera

